{"timestamp": "2025-12-05 19:01:57.132618", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Solution submitted.\n\nSummary of submission:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: host_1, vpn_server_1, external_router_1\n- root_cause_name: host_vpn_membership_missing, host_incorrect_ip\n\nIf you want, I can now:\n- Provide specific remediation steps to bring up the WireGuard tunnel (check peer configs, keys, allowed-ips, endpoint/port, and service logs) and steps to stop external_router_1 from advertising the 20.0.0.0/24 network into RIP (remove that network stanza or apply route filtering/policy).\n- Collect WireGuard logs and peer configuration files from host_1 and vpn_server_1, and the FRR config from external_router_1 to make a prescriptive change set.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2441, "output_tokens": 165, "total_tokens": 2606, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
